column1: #Text=Maroochydore is a city on the Sunshine Coast of Queensland .
#Text=See Sunshine Coast guide for how to get into the region .
#Text=Car is by far the easiest way to see most attractions in a short amount of time , or at your own pace .
#Text=Larger car hire companies may offer relocations to Brisbane Airport or the Gold Coast .
#Text=Try the major national renters with services at Maroochy Airport or other local independents that hire new cars .
#Text=The Sunshine Coast is part of the south east Queensland translink area .
#Text=Sunshine Plaza is a hub for the bus services in the area .
#Text=Walk across the Maroochy River bridge to Chambers Island
#Text=Farmer 's market with street food and music .
#Text=A shopping mall with large outdoor areas around a waterway .
#Text=Normal chain stores are represented , but there are also paddle boats and quite a few eateries alfresco style .
#Text=Brews their own IPA , available on tap .
#Text=Maroochy River Resort & Bungalows ( Maroochy River Bungalows ) , 38-46 David Low Way , Maroochydore ( behind the Waterfront Hotel & BWS ) , ☏ +61754484911 .
#Text=Private boat ramp , kayaks , tennis , bbqs , pools , sunlounges .
#Text=Close to the action but away from the rat race .
#Text=Apartment-style accommodation on Maroochydore beach , views of the beach , river and hinterland .
#Text=There is free internet at the Library .
#Text=Maroochydore Towing Service Accident and emergency vehicle recovery , Sunshine Coast areas 24hr service .
